{"tid":2207974,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大三罷當天涉黃大仙非法集結 事隔逾年兩青年被控","createTime":"2020-09-18T13:44:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T18:19:24.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b3a08e468748cc16a7b46192a4382a96d603a4bc","tid":2207974,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T13:44:29.000Z","msg":"網民去年8月5日「大三罷」，全港多區有示威者堵路。事隔超過一年後，有17歲男生與19歲男侍應被指當日在黃大仙參與非法集結，案件今在觀塘裁判法院提堂。主任裁判官徐綺薇將案件押後至下月30日再訊，以待辯方索取文件及提供法律意見，並下令屆時辯方須表明答辯意向。<br />\n<br />\n兩被告依序為17歲林姓男學生及19歲侍應林繼達，他們被指於去年8月5日在黃大仙公共運輸交匯處附近參與非法集結。徐官批准兩人分別以500元及1,000元保釋候訊，其間須宵禁、不准離港、每周向警署報到。<br />\n<br />\n此外，17歲劉姓男學生被指於今年8月7日在將軍澳廣場一樓東海堂，與其他人破壞屬於美心食品公司的兩個顯示屏及一個陳列櫥窗玻璃，被控刑事毁壞罪。案件今在觀塘法院提堂，押後至下月16日再訊，以待辯方索取文件，其間劉獲准保釋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200918/IJNJEFSE5VAURC55VFHURS32GY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200918%2FIJNJEFSE5VAURC55VFHURS32GY%2F&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdUzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=6e1b9aec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200918%2FIJNJEFSE5VAURC55VFHURS32GY%2F&h=890030ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200918/IJNJEFSE5VAURC55VFHURS32GY/</a>"},{"pid":"6b278435651985bde96d934b8e9c175a852df232","tid":2207974,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T13:53:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca7ff642b6d595e5aa482b425f37389614e2de6","tid":2207974,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b278435651985bde96d934b8e9c175a852df232","tid":2207974,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T13:53:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/